title: The World's First Ever Transgender Doll Is Here
text:
Jazz Jennings was only 5 years old when she announced to her family that she identified as female, becoming one of the youngest publicly documented people to be identified as transgender, as well as one of the youngest trans icons for people all around the world. But although Jazz, like many little girls, loved dolls growing up, she could never find one that represented her. Now, that's all going to change for a brand new generation of kids.
